net.explorviz.security.util

Class PasswordStorage

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.explorviz.security.util.PasswordStorage

  • public class PasswordStorage
extends java.lang.Object
    This repository contains peer-reviewed libraries for password storage. Passwords are "hashed" with PBKDF2 (64,000 iterations of SHA1 by default) using a cryptographically-random salt.
    See Also:
    https://github.com/defuse/password-hashing
